STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Steven ALICEA, a/k/a Steven J. Alicea, Allica Steven, Lil Steven, and Lil Shine, Defendant-Petitioner. C-840 September Term 2018
082005 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 3, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001363-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
